Run script/cider_server.pl to test the application.


To make changes to the database schema:

1. Make changes to the appropriate column definitions in the Perl DBIC
class file(s) in lib/CIDER/Schema/Result/.

2. Run "script/cider_ddl.pl" to generate a new version of cider.sql.

3. Run "svn diff cider.sql --diff-cmd script/cider_sqlt_diff.pl" to
generate a sequence of SQL commands reflecting the changes.

4. Update your MySQL database by entering the above commands at the
mysql command prompt.

